---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Features - letsorder"
  description="Explore the powerful features of letsorder, designed to streamline your restaurant management and enhance the customer experience."
>
  <!-- Restaurant Manager Features -->
  <section id="manager-features" class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">For Restaurant Managers</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          A comprehensive suite of tools to manage your restaurant efficiently, from menu updates to order tracking.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <!-- Restaurant Management -->
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm border">
          <img src="/src/assets/restaurant-dashboard.svg" alt="Restaurant Dashboard" class="w-full h-48 object-cover rounded-md mb-6" />
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Restaurant Management</h3>
          <ul class="text-gray-600 space-y-2">
            <li>Register and manage multiple restaurant profiles.</li>
            <li>Update details like name, address, and Google Maps link.</li>
            <li>Requires at least 2 managers for registration.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Manager Permissions -->
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm border">
          <img src="/src/assets/manager-permissions.svg" alt="Manager Permissions" class="w-full h-48 object-cover rounded-md mb-6" />
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Manager & Team Collaboration</h3>
          <ul class="text-gray-600 space-y-2">
            <li>Invite managers via a secure invitation system.</li>
            <li>Role-based permissions for granular control.</li>
            <li>Super admin role for full access management.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Menu Management -->
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm border">
          <img src="/src/assets/menu-management.svg" alt="Menu Management Interface" class="w-full h-48 object-cover rounded-md mb-6" />
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Dynamic Menu Management</h3>
          <ul class="text-gray-600 space-y-2">
            <li>Create and organize menu sections and items.</li>
            <li>Drag-and-drop reordering for easy updates.</li>
            <li>Toggle item availability in real-time.</li>
            <li>Bulk operations for efficient management.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Table & QR Code Management -->
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm border">
          <img src="/src/assets/qr-code-generation.svg" alt="QR Code Generation" class="w-full h-48 object-cover rounded-md mb-6" />
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Table & QR Code Management</h3>
          <ul class="text-gray-600 space-y-2">
            <li>Create and manage tables or rooms.</li>
            <li>Generate unique QR codes for each table.</li>
            <li>Bulk QR code generation and printing support.</li>
            <li>Regenerate QR codes for enhanced security.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Order Management -->
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm border">
          <img src="/src/assets/order-tracking-dashboard.svg" alt="Order Tracking Dashboard" class="w-full h-48 object-cover rounded-md mb-6" />
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Real-Time Order Tracking</h3>
          <ul class="text-gray-600 space-y-2">
            <li>View and track orders as they come in.</li>
            <li>Manage order status from pending to delivered.</li>
            <li>Filter orders by date, status, or table.</li>
            <li>Access order statistics and analytics.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Table Management -->
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm border">
          <img src="/src/assets/table-management.svg" alt="Table Management" class="w-full h-48 object-cover rounded-md mb-6" />
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Table Management</h3>
          <ul class="text-gray-600 space-y-2">
            <li>Organize your restaurant layout with tables and rooms.</li>
            <li>Assign names or numbers for easy identification.</li>
            <li>Link tables directly to QR codes for seamless ordering.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Customer Features -->
  <section id="customer-features" class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">For Your Customers</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          A seamless and modern dining experience for your guests, accessible from any smartphone.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-gray-50 p-8 rounded-lg border">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Instant Menu Access</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Customers scan a QR code to instantly view your menu. No app download required.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gray-50 p-8 rounded-lg border">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Simple Ordering</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">An intuitive interface allows customers to browse the menu and place orders directly from their table.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gray-50 p-8 rounded-lg border">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Real-Time Updates</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">The menu always reflects the latest item availability, ensuring a smooth ordering process.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Technical Specifications -->
  <section id="tech-specs" class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Security & Reliability</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Built on a robust and secure foundation to ensure your data is safe and your service is always available.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm border">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Secure Authentication</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">JWT-based authentication ensures that only authorized managers can access the admin dashboard.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm border">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Role-Based Access Control</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Fine-grained permissions control what each manager can see and do.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm border">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Database Backups</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Litestream provides continuous, real-time backups of your database to a secure, off-site location.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm border">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Error Monitoring</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Integrated with Sentry for real-time error tracking and performance monitoring.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm border">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Modern Tech Stack</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Backend built with Rust (Actix Web) for performance and reliability. Admin app built with SolidJS for a fast user experience.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm border">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Guest-Friendly</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">The customer-facing menu is a lightweight Astro application, ensuring fast load times on any device.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
